#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:1
msgid "DMN Validator"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:3
msgid ""
"The DMN Validator lets you validate one or more DMN files against the RONL "
"DMN+ syntactic layers before publishing them to TriplyDB. It is accessible "
"from the shield icon (🛡) in the sidebar."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:12
msgid "Multi-file validation"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:14
msgid ""
"You can drop any number of `.dmn` or `.xml` files onto the validator at "
"once, or add files incrementally — the drop zone remains visible at the top "
"of the panel whenever files are loaded. Files are validated independently "
"and displayed side-by-side for easy comparison."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:16
msgid "Each file card shows:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:18
msgid "File name and size"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:19
msgid "A **Validate** button to trigger validation for that file individually"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:20
msgid ""
"A **Validate all** button in the header to validate all loaded files at once"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:21
msgid ""
"The validation result with a summary badge and collapsible layer sections"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:22
msgid "A remove (×) button to dismiss the file"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:24
msgid ""
"Navigation state is preserved: switching to another view (SPARQL editor, "
"chain builder, etc.) and returning does not clear the loaded files or their "
"results."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:28
msgid "Validation layers"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:30
msgid ""
"Results are grouped into five layers. Each layer can be expanded to see "
"individual issues. Issues carry a severity, a typed code, and a human-"
"readable message."
